rote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />- Had no idea that pressing UP + B shoots the special item fireball. Maybe state this somewhere so players know. <br /><br /></div><br /><br />I had some remarks about UP+B or DOWN+A, I may add a mini in-game tutorial to explain it clearly.<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">Erockbrox wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />- I love the intro level screens. Reminds me of the Sonic 1,2 games. <br /><br />- Music and graphics are outstanding.</div><br /><br />Again, thanks <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

